description:
This is a 6 minute workout called 'Core Burn Express' from the channel Christie Wang.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Pilates.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Masterclass Workout vibe.
The The Masterclass Workout vibe means Technique-driven, focused, skill-building. This is especially good for Those who love precision and mastery in movement..
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Ignite your core in this quick and efficient Pilates session with Christie. 

Note: A thick towel or blanket is recommended. ...
